    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Screeps: Arena</strong> 是一款仅支持在线 PvP 的游戏，你的脚本会在 1v1 的匹配制竞技场环境中自动与其他玩家的脚本战斗。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略与编程的结合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏拥有经典 RTS 所具备的全部战略深度，包括 <strong>资源采集、基地建设和单位生产</strong>。但它有一个革命性的转折：你并不直接控制你的单位。相反，你通过编写在游戏服务器上运行的完整 JavaScript 程序来进行游戏，由它自动执行你的宏大战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/50334a35d3317f84d15ab450bc64984f.poster.avif?t=1772039787\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/50334a35d3317f84d15ab450bc64984f.webm?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/50334a35d3317f84d15ab450bc64984f.mp4?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >易于上手，难于精通</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只需要<strong>基础的编程技能</strong>就能开始，但游戏提供了一个深度复杂的环境，让高级程序员也能将自己的能力发挥到极致。虽然 JavaScript 是原生语言，你仍可以使用社区支持的 TypeScript、Python、Rust、C#、Kotlin 等语言的相关包（详见 Steam 指南）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/0ed04ab4700367d46d7b28c5ec4dfb55.poster.avif?t=1772039787\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/0ed04ab4700367d46d7b28c5ec4dfb55.webm?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/0ed04ab4700367d46d7b28c5ec4dfb55.mp4?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全天候的竞技场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的代码会在一系列短小而节奏紧凑的 1v1 对局中与其他玩家的脚本交锋。系统会根据你的竞技场评分自动为你匹配<strong>实力相近的对手</strong>。最棒的是，你几乎可以在<strong>任何时间、瞬间</strong>找到旗鼓相当的对局。即使没有玩家在线，系统也会使用他们保存的代码为你提供持续不断的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/fbd712e826edf7c04b782bb0f99752d6.poster.avif?t=1772039787\" width=1170 height=460 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/fbd712e826edf7c04b782bb0f99752d6.webm?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/fbd712e826edf7c04b782bb0f99752d6.mp4?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索不同的“竞技场”——每一种都是独特的多人游戏模式，拥有自己的规则和战略目标。为了保持竞争的新鲜感，我们会在每个赛季引入<strong>全新的竞技场</strong>，迫使你不断适应，并为不同挑战编写新代码。通过每日名望获取资源并打造物品，以解锁更多内容，或者与朋友一起游玩并设计你们自己的私人挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/8940cf1a85715a176d72947476f07031.poster.avif?t=1772039787\" width=800 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/8940cf1a85715a176d72947476f07031.webm?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1137320/extras/8940cf1a85715a176d72947476f07031.mp4?t=1772039787\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
